{"tid":473850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深宵開枱無有怕　日本網民百潔布製「無噪音麻雀」獲激讚","createTime":"2017-11-19T14:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T17:31:01.000Z","uid":732,"like":391,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"3b45c413c214d52af92c39c61d243338280f11d9","tid":473850,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"香港住宅密度高，加上有噪音管制，「麻雀」玩家手癮起想多打兩圈至深夜，都會被鄰居投訴。日本有網民利用百潔布創作出「無噪音麻雀」，開枱摸牌打幾圈，把牌子大大力拍在枱上都不會發出甚麼聲音，可以放心打牌打通宵，圖片迅速在網上瘋傳，不少人都稱「想要返套」。惟有網民表示，打牌最過癮就是聽到牌子拍到枱上的響亮聲音，「而且打牌最嘈係人聲」，認為百潔布麻雀始終不及打真牌有質感。<br />\n<br />\n日本網民isaki&rlm;昨日在Twitter上載一張相片，顯示有4人開枱打麻雀，惟牌子較一般大，原來是由一塊塊百潔布製成，卻可以如真麻雀般疊牌，的確可當真牌打，但牌面看來是平面的，似乎難以靠指尖去「摸牌」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民大讚此發明「創意爆燈」、製作人是「天才」，紛紛表示想擁有一套。早前有研究指出，打麻將可減低患腦退化症的風險，有網民稱，日本長者多，「百潔布麻將」體積較大，更方便老人家看到，又不用怕小孩子誤吞，看護中心都應常備幾套。<br />\n<br />\n不過亦有人擔心「百潔布麻將」太輕身，有機會被風吹倒，而沒有「牌品」的玩家，更可趁別人「出銃」時開風扇擾亂雀局。另亦網民笑稱，擔心玩家會悄悄地在牌上沾上洗潔清「出貓」。<br />\n<br />\n樓主的創意成功「拋磚引玉」，其他網民陸續提出以不同物料製造麻將，例如有學生稱利用擦膠製小型麻雀，就可悄悄在校內「開枱」，不過學生哥還是乖乖上課吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/992410/xlarge/2a48867294542b9530488a8ff0702888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F992410%2Fxlarge%2F2a48867294542b9530488a8ff0702888.jpg&h=633e8e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/992433/xlarge/afa1bb352ab6e70fb0ab90aaba934719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F992433%2Fxlarge%2Fafa1bb352ab6e70fb0ab90aaba934719.jpg&h=d12f7908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民指「百潔布麻將」體積較大，更方便老人家看到。（SQureha ekimemo Twitter 圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/992434/xlarge/062b1dc676a62950ae6cbcc5652079ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F992434%2Fxlarge%2F062b1dc676a62950ae6cbcc5652079ba.jpg&h=ca0da5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/992412/xlarge/04686d4b7e82cd12989d63939bf0118f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F992412%2Fxlarge%2F04686d4b7e82cd12989d63939bf0118f.jpg&h=45c5da20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04fe467265069eda0d9c81d6fcd757fc38e0204a","tid":473850,"uid":89182,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"9c30122e4837b8727af87605bc1d03658d8f5773","tid":473850,"uid":37153,"like":77,"dislike":88,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"打麻雀keep住靜好無聊"},{"pid":"52561c39343179f87a5cb1100e5e91030ef480a2","tid":473850,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好得意"},{"pid":"1420f5669cfbde161e540787ebc92493d4aff67a","tid":473850,"uid":71058,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"無得甩牌"},{"pid":"23ff3e5452c43eef94f0a7ae1ed15e031a49cc88","tid":473850,"uid":44562,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"要戴手套洗牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7237144625056021a2d63b45063f14abe71400e6","tid":473850,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"日本大神真係好乾淨企理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7193feac7ca896a874d89b60b6ce37f45d4fa05e","tid":473850,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"即場印牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86197ec836e0a23197a5702471ab706c01305a6d","tid":473850,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"賭錢&hellip